{"_path":"/maps/_computer/encoding/emoji","_dir":"encoding","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Emoji","description":"Emoji 是一种表情符号，是一种用来在电子通信中传达情感的符号。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"javascript-下含有-emoji-字符串的处理"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"link","props":{"type":"h5","to":"https://mgear-file.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/JavaScript%E4%B8%8B%E5%90%AB%E6%9C%89emoji%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%20-%20%E6%8E%98%E9%87%91.html","source":"https://juejin.cn/post/6941276804472635405"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"《JavaScript 下含有 emoji 字符串的处理》"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在处理 emoji 字符时有些坑。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"String 原型上的 length、split、substr 等函数不能正确计算带 emoji 字符串"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"展开运算符会把组合 emoji 拆开"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"另一些坑可使用常规方法规避。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"String 原型上的 charAt 和 fromCharCode 函数可分别使用 ES6 新增的 charPointAt、fromCharPoint 代替"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"字符串遍历 for...in 可以使用 for...of 代替"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"正则匹配时可以在后面加一个 unicode 标记"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"从-unicode-到-emoji"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"link","props":{"type":"h5","to":"https://mgear-file.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/%E4%BB%8EUnicode%E5%88%B0emoji%20-%20%E7%9F%A5%E4%B9%8E.html","source":"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/41203455"},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"《从 Unicode 到 emoji》"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ASCII 使用一个字节来编码，所以远远不够用，但因为它的编码集只占用了 128 种，所以一个字节开头的高位就用不上了。所以类似 GBK 字符集的解决方案是如果高位是 0 那么就是一字节的英文字符，否则使用连续的两字节来表示其他字符，这种方案叫做“代码页”。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不过代码页不好用，因为在不同的操作系统、不同的厂商、软件中代码页不尽相同，所以后来出现了 Unicode，它尝试将世界上所有的字符统一编码。Unicode 一开始是两个字节的，后来不够用才变成了四个字节。传输的时候为了不要传输那么多“0”，所以需要对编码进行序列化及压缩。所以后来出现了 UTF 这种编码方式。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Emoji 就更好玩了，出现了一些特殊的用法："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用单色修饰符确定 emoji 是单色还是彩色的，如 ⚠︎ === U+26A0 + U+FE0E，⚠️ === U+26A0 + U+FE0F"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用肤色修饰符确定 emoji 中出现的人物的肤色，如 🧒 === U+1f9d2，🧒🏿 === U+1f9d2 + U+1f3ff"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用零宽连接符 U+200D 将不同的 emoji 组合起来成为一个单独的符号（不支持的系统会自动回退为多个 emoji）"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"todo"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TODO"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://tao.zz.ac/utf-8.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《UTF-8 往事》"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://tao.zz.ac/emoji.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《Emoji 的奥秘》"}]}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"todo","depth":2,"text":"TODO"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_computer:encoding:emoji.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_computer/encoding/emoji.md","_stem":"6.maps/_computer/encoding/emoji","_extension":"md"}